{"word":"Judas","slug":"judas","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Judas</b> 1. Surnamed Iscariot:<br/> - Chosen as an apostle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=4'>Mat 10:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=19'>Mar 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=16'>Luk 6:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=17'>Act 1:17</a> <br/> - Treasurer of the disciples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=6'>Joh 12:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=29'>Joh 13:29</a> <br/> - His covetousness exemplified:<br/> b by his protest against the breaking of the box of ointment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=6'>Joh 12:6</a><br/> b by his bargain to betray Jesus for a sum of money<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=16'>Mat 26:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=11'>Mar 14:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=6'>Luk 22:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=2'>Joh 13:2</a><br/> - His apostasy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=17&verse=12'>Joh 17:12</a> <br/> - Betrays the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=50'>Mat 26:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=45'>Mar 14:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=49'>Luk 22:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=5'>Joh 18:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=25'>Act 1:25</a> <br/> - Returns the money to the rulers of the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=10'>Mat 27:10</a> <br/> - Hangs himself<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=5'>Mat 27:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=18'>Act 1:18</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=25'>Mat 26:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=21'>Mar 14:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=23'>Luk 22:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=26'>Joh 13:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=17&verse=12'>Joh 17:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=16'>Act 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=20'>Act 1:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=41&verse=9'>Psa 41:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=109&verse=8'>Psa 109:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=11&verse=13'>Zec 11:13</a> <br/> 2. One of the &#187;brethren&#171; of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=55'>Mat 13:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=3'>Mar 6:3</a><br/> 3. Brother of James and writer of the Epistle of Jude<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=16'>Luk 6:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a>; <a href='B:'></a><br/> 4. An apostle, probably identical with Lebbaeus, or Thaddaeus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=14&verse=22'>Joh 14:22</a><br/> 5. Of Galilee, who stirred up a sedition among the Jews soon after the birth of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=37'>Act 5:37</a><br/> 6. A disciple who entertained Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=11'>Act 9:11</a><br/> 7. Surnamed Barsabas, a Christian sent to Antioch with Paul and Barnabas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=32'>Act 15:32</a>"}]}